  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a varied continental breakfast for its guests. For those opting for the half board upgrade, the hotel has two restaurants, both with sea views. One can be found in the main hotel and the other in the tower.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
