  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>There are two restaurants at Hotl Luna Convento, both offering traditional dishes inspired by local ingredients and with terraces with stunning panoramic sea views. A bar offers a selection of international and local drinks.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s saltwater pool is set into the cliffs with uninterrupted sea views. It’s accessed by around 80 steps.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Wifi </li>
<li>Garage - apporx. €20 per day, payable locally</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
